Anosike Victor Ementa (amụrụ na 3 Mee 2002) bụ onye Danish ọkachamara na-agba bọọlụ nke sitere na Naijiria, onye na-agba ọsọ dị ka onye na-aga n'ihu maka Danish Superliga club AaB
Ementa bụ ngwaahịa nke B71 Sandoy
Ementa emeela nke mbụ ya na Danish reserve league mgbe ọ dị afọ iri na ise megide ndị otu F.C

Copenhagen n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ afọ 2017. Na Nọvemba 2019, Ementa bịanyere aka na nkwekọrịta ọhụrụ na Helsingør. O nwetara egwuregwu izizi ya maka klọb ahụ na 4 Julaị 2020 na egwuregwu egwuregwu egwuregwu nke abụọ nke Danish megide Jammerbugt FC.
A kwalitere Helsingør na ngalaba nke mbụ nke Danish maka oge 2020-21
Ementa pụtara ugboro abụọ na 1st Division na Disemba 2020, tupu e ree ya.
Na 27 Jenụwarị 2021 Danish Superliga club AaB kwadoro, na ha abanyela Ementa na nkwekọrịta ruo na njedebe nke 2023
Ementa bu n'obi na mbụ maka ọrụ na otu U-19 club
Agbanyeghị, ọ jisiri ike mee mpụta mbụ ya maka ndị otu U-19 na oge izizi ya, ka ọ gachara n'April 2021 ịwa ahụ maka mgbaji ike gwụrụ na obere mkpịsị ụkwụ ya.

N'agbanyeghị nke ahụ, na June 2021, a kwalitere ya na ndị otu mbụ. N'abalị iri abụọ na abụọ n'ọnwa Nọvemba n'afọ 2021, Ementa nwetara akara izizi ya maka AaB megide SønderjyskE na Danish Superliga. Ementa bịara na nkeji nke 89 wee nwee ike inye aka maka goolu ikpeazụ AaB.
A mụrụ ya na Denmark, Ementa bụ onye Naijiria.
